---

---

<section
  id="about"
  class="relative py-40 bg-[#040406] text-white overflow-hidden"
>
  <!-- Minimalist Grid Background -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03] pointer-events-none"
    style="background-image: linear-gradient(#fff 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, #fff 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 40px 40px;"
    data-parallax
    data-speed="0.02"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="w-[85%] max-w-[1800px] mx-auto relative z-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-20 items-start">
      <!-- Typography / Manifesto Section -->
      <div class="lg:w-1/2 space-y-16">
        <div>
          <h2
            class="text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-[#ffcc33] mb-6 reveal-fade-up"
          >
            Corporate Profile
          </h2>
          <h3
            class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold leading-[0.95] tracking-tight text-white reveal-fade-up delay-100"
          >
            STRATEGIC <br />
            ENGINEERING <br />
            <span class="text-[#25c4ff]">AT SCALE.</span>
          </h3>
        </div>

        <div class="h-px w-full bg-white/10 reveal-fade-up delay-150"></div>

        <div
          class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 text-[#c8d2dc] font-light leading-relaxed reveal-fade-up delay-200"
        >
          <p>
            En Fantasma Digital, redefinimos la infraestructura empresarial
            moderna. Alejándonos de las soluciones convencionales, implementamos
            arquitecturas de software de alto rendimiento diseñadas para la
            escalabilidad global y la resiliencia crítica.
          </p>
          <p>
            Nuestra metodología integra consultoría de élite con ejecución
            técnica de precisión. No solo escribimos código; diseñamos el
            sistema nervioso digital que impulsará su organización durante la
            próxima década.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-12 pt-8 reveal-fade-up delay-300">
          <div>
            <div class="text-6xl font-bold text-white tracking-tighter mb-1">
              500<span class="text-[#ffcc33] text-4xl align-top">+</span>
            </div>
            <div
              class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-500 font-semibold"
            >
              Engineers
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="w-px h-16 bg-white/10"></div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-6xl font-bold text-white tracking-tighter mb-1">
              3<span class="text-[#25c4ff] text-4xl align-top">HQ</span>
            </div>
            <div
              class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-500 font-semibold"
            >
              Global Hubs
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Tech Visual / Image Section -->
      <div
        class="lg:w-1/2 w-full mt-10 lg:mt-0 reveal-scale-up delay-200"
        data-parallax
        data-speed="-0.05"
      >
        <div
          class="relative w-full aspect-[16/9] lg:aspect-square bg-[#0a0f16] border border-white/5 overflow-hidden group"
        >
          {/* Background Image - Strategic Software Engineering (Code focus) */}
          <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center opacity-30 grayscale transition-all duration-1000 group-hover:scale-105 group-hover:opacity-50 group-hover:grayscale-0"
            style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555066931-4365d14bab8c?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop');"
          >
          </div>

          <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-[#040406] via-[#040406]/60 to-[#25c4ff]/5"
          >
          </div>

          <!-- Software Architecture Grid Overlay -->
          <div
            class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10 pointer-events-none"
            style="background-image: radial-gradient(#25c4ff 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 30px 30px;"
          >
          </div>

          {/* Floating Brackets/Code Elements */}
          <div
            class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden opacity-20 pointer-events-none font-mono text-[10px] text-[#25c4ff] p-6 flex flex-col gap-2"
          >
            <div class="reveal-fade-in delay-500">
              class StrategicArchitecture &#123;
            </div>
            <div class="reveal-fade-in delay-700 ml-4">
              public deploy() &#123; return "Scale"; &#125;
            </div>
            <div class="reveal-fade-in delay-900">&#125;</div>
            <div
              class="absolute top-10 right-10 text-4xl font-light opacity-30"
            >
              &#123; &#125;
            </div>
            <div
              class="absolute bottom-40 right-20 text-2xl font-light transform rotate-12 opacity-30"
            >
              &lt; / &gt;
            </div>
          </div>

          <div
            class="absolute bottom-8 left-8 p-6 bg-[#040406]/90 backdrop-blur border-l-2 border-[#ffcc33]"
          >
            <p class="text-xs font-mono text-[#25c4ff] mb-2">
              LATEST DEPLOYMENT
            </p>
            <p class="text-white font-bold text-lg">Banking Core Refactor</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-1">London, UK — Q4 2024</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
